  <scopecontent id="aspace_c0ad79fc4775eedd9daeb1ca46687c08">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Newspapers and magazines reporting events of WWI including the Armistice being signed (Nov. 1918) and major events during World War II (1941-49), including the <title>Washington Times Herald</title>; <title>Washington Post</title>; <title>New York Times</title>; <title>Baltimore News-Post</title>; <title>Washington Daily News</title>; <title>Philadelphia Inquirer</title>; <title>Daily Mirror</title>; <title>Baltimore American</title>; <title>Evening Star</title>; <title>Minneapolis Journal</title>; <title>Wisconsin State Journal</title>; <title>Madison Democrat</title>; <title>Yank: the Army Weekly</title> and <title>The Voice of Victory</title>; <title>Star Herald</title> (1945); <title>Panama Morning Journal</title> (1914).</p>  </scopecontent>
